The global burden of typhoid and paratyphoid fevers: a systematic analysis for 
the Global Burden of Disease Study 2017.

GBD 2017 Typhoid and Paratyphoid Collaborators.

Collaborators: Stanaway JD, Reiner RC, Blacker BF, Goldberg EM, Khalil IA, 
Troeger CE, Andrews JR, Bhutta ZA, Crump JA, Im J, Marks F, Mintz E, Park SE, 
Zaidi AKM, Abebe Z, Abejie AN, Adedeji IA, Ali BA, Amare AT, Atalay HT, Avokpaho 
