CausalTAB: the PSI-MITAB 2.8 updated format for signalling data representation 
and dissemination.

Perfetto L(1)(2), Acencio ML(3), Bradley G(4), Cesareni G(1)(5), Del Toro N(2), 
Fazekas D(6)(7), Hermjakob H(2)(8), Korcsmaros T(7)(9), Kuiper M(10), Lægreid 
A(3), Lo Surdo P(1), Lovering RC(11), Orchard S(2), Porras P(2), Thomas PD(12), 
Touré V(10), Zobolas J(10), Licata L(1).

Author information:
(1)Department of Biology, University of Rome Tor Vergata, Rome, Italy.
(2)European Molecular Biology Laboratory, European Bioinformatics Institute 
(EMBL-EBI), Hinxton, Cambridge, UK.
(3)Department of Clinical and Molecular Medicine, Norwegian University of 
Science and Technology (NTNU), Trondheim, Norway.
(4)Computational Biology and Statistics, Target Sciences, GSK, UK.
(5)IRCCS, Fondazione Santa Lucia, Rome, Italy.
(6)Department of Genetics, Eötvös Loránd University, Budapest, Hungary.
(7)Earlham Institute, Norwich, UK.
(8)State Key Laboratory of Proteomics, Beijing Institute of Life Omics, Beijing 
Proteome Research Center, National Center for Protein Sciences, Beijing, China.
(9)Quadram Institute, Norwich, UK.
(10)Department of Biology, Norwegian University of Science and Technology 
