Life expectancy of follicular lymphoma patients in complete response at 
30 months is similar to that of the Spanish general population.

Magnano L(1)(2), Alonso-Alvarez S(3), Alcoceba M(2)(3), Rivas-Delgado A(1)(2), 
Muntañola A(4), Nadeu F(5), Setoain X(6), Rodríguez S(6), Andrade-Campos M(7), 
