Influence of body size, topography, food availability and tree-fall gaps on 
space use by yellow-footed tortoises (Chelonoidis denticulatus) in Central 
Amazonia.

Tavares AS(1), Morcatty TQ(1)(2), Zuanon J(3), Magnusson WE(3).
